p.d: After a few years in Ibiza yoga instructor Chrystal Sinn has finally found the perfect location for her very own yoga retreat. A stunning mansion that boasts many luxuries, Chrystal's new paradise is the ideal get away for her clients where they can relax, unwind, practice yoga and of course fuck! Just ask Marica Chanelle, a work addict who's in need of a break, or Lika Star and Alberto Blanco, a couple that needs to reignite the passion. And what of Chrystal herself, she could use a little one on one session with her boyfriend too. Whether it's yoga or sex, everything has a solution and you can watch our stars prove it as they suck and fuck the stress away right here in Private Gold, Sexy Yoga in Paradise.
